      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Old GSTR-1, GSTR-3B and GSTR-9 data should be archived as PDF/JSON exports from Tally and stored alongside the migrated ledger. Future GST returns are filed from the cloud system. The two histories link via invoice number and GSTIN.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

